{"tid":2010381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲用即日民調數字進行配票?其實我地每人天生已經擁有一個配票號碼","createTime":"2020-05-10T11:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T04:55:45.000Z","uid":19648,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e9fd66266aeca8a6ec19dd35edbe40eb265d836c","tid":2010381,"uid":19648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"就係身份証號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議實行方法:<br />\n先假設身份証號尾數(不包括號內數字)是平均及包括數字 01 至 99 (希望有入境手足可以證實)<br />\n以新界東為例，目標為五席取三席。 以身份証號尾數(不包括號內數字)進行分組配票<br />\n例如: 01 ~ 32 投一位候選人， 34 ~ 66 投一位候選人，67 ~ 99 投一位候選人<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，歡迎討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另見一個POST:<br />\n所有初選候選人同意簽「攬炒書」！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2010154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2010154</a>"},{"pid":"792e628b45749a2fe55a4c80334d4c29cf3bfa14","tid":2010381,"uid":114792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"生日月份似可行啲<br />\n簡單啲唔會搞錯<br />\n又有得計番邊幾個月份多人出世啲<br />\n人口普查唔知有冇"},{"pid":"de68e4f52fe71914c1741c4d0e81f4cb87e04c8e","tid":2010381,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e9fd66266aeca8a6ec19dd35edbe40eb265d836c","tid":2010381,"uid":19648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"就係身份証號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg